Class Notification

java.lang.Object
com.group6.hms.app.notifications.Notification
public class Notification extends Object
The Notification class represents a notification within the system. It includes a title, message, timestamp, and user ID to identify the intended recipient.

  • Constructor Details

    • Notification

      public Notification(String title, String message, UUID userID)
      Constructs a new Notification with the specified title, message, and user ID. The timestamp is set to the current date and time.
      Parameters:
      title - the title of the notification
      message - the message content of the notification
      userID - the unique identifier of the user receiving the notification

    • Notification

      public Notification(String title, String message, LocalDateTime timestamp, UUID userID)
      Constructs a new Notification with the specified title, message, timestamp, and user ID.
      Parameters:
      title - the title of the notification
      message - the message content of the notification
      timestamp - the time when the notification was created
      userID - the unique identifier of the user receiving the notification
